# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# HelixOnix Core API — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env and fill in your values
# ALL vars are validated at startup via Zod — app refuses to start if any are missing
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── App ──────────────────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000
HOST=0.0.0.0
API_VERSION=v1
LOG_LEVEL=info

# ── Database (PostgreSQL 15 + pgvector) ──────────
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/helixonix?sslmode=require
DATABASE_POOL_MAX=20
DATABASE_POOL_MIN=5

# ── Redis ─────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://default:password@localhost:6379

# ── Auth ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Generate: openssl rand -base64 64
JWT_SECRET=64879b466af8076f44b0c2c07c9bd194e3b979b32371451336467555fec775a2
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=9cb6ec0ada6aa9e6564180674e0be53bf32013c9f55121a62f7ffa9eb2b57dbb
JWT_ACCESS_TTL=900
JWT_REFRESH_TTL=2592000
ARGON2_MEMORY=65536

# OAuth
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=403367704866-875jbqbas69gpaudqtqcsspc2l2nrv6d.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=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

# ── Stripe ────────────────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
STRIPE_CONNECT_CLIENT_ID=ca_...

# Stripe Price IDs (create in Stripe dashboard)
STRIPE_PRICE_BUYER_PRO=price_...
STRIPE_PRICE_BUYER_TEAM=price_...
STRIPE_PRICE_SELLER_CREATOR=price_...
STRIPE_PRICE_SELLER_PRO=price_...
STRIPE_PRICE_SELLER_STUDIO=price_...
STRIPE_PRICE_CREDITS_100=price_...
STRIPE_PRICE_CREDITS_500=price_...
STRIPE_PRICE_CREDITS_2000=price_...

# ── Cloudflare R2 (S3-compatible) ─────────────────
R2_ACCOUNT_ID=your-account-id
R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-access-key-id
R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-secret-access-key
R2_BUCKET_NAME=helixonix-assets
R2_PUBLIC_URL=https://cdn.helixonix.com
MAX_UPLOAD_SIZE_MB=500

# ── AI Services ───────────────────────────────────
REPLICATE_API_KEY=r8_...
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=...
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── Typesense ─────────────────────────────────────
TYPESENSE_HOST=localhost
TYPESENSE_PORT=8108
TYPESENSE_PROTOCOL=http
TYPESENSE_API_KEY=your-typesense-api-key
TYPESENSE_SEARCH_ONLY_KEY=your-search-only-key

# ── Email (Resend) ────────────────────────────────
RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@helixonix.com
EMAIL_SUPPORT=support@helixonix.com

# ── Internal Services ─────────────────────────────
HELIX_BRAIN_URL=http://localhost:3001
HELIX_BRAIN_INTERNAL_SECRET=your-helix-brain-internal-secret-min-32-chars
INTERNAL_API_SECRET=your-internal-api-secret-min-32-chars

# ── CORS ─────────────────────────────────────────
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:5174,http://localhost:5175

# ── URLs ─────────────────────────────────────────
BUYER_URL=https://helixonix.com
CREATOR_URL=https://create.helixonix.com
ADMIN_URL=https://admin.helixonix.com

# ── Monitoring ────────────────────────────────────
SENTRY_DSN=https://...@sentry.io/...
SENTRY_ENVIRONMENT=development
